stimulus:
Welcome to this 1 min. survey on daily rhythms, body and mood.

You will be asked to report your heart-rate

and given some questions about yourself.

Take the test when prompted and/or at different times of the day/night.

Please make a personal ID (three letters+ two numbers, e.g. ept23).

Write it down and use this ID whenever taking the test.
How Sad/Angry or Happy are you right now?
How Tired/Sleepy/Distracted or Fresh/Awake/Alert are you right now?
How Hungry or Satiated are you right now?
